      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Soft or Spotty?",
        "Client": "Lady in Distress",
        "Description": "I\u0027m trying to come up with the\r\ndesign for a new dress, and I\r\nwant to base it on a monster!\r\nThe fluffy Gowngoat, or the\r\ncute li\u0027l spotted Boggi, which\r\nshould I choose!? I can\u0027t decide!\r\nGo and check them out, please!",
        "Target": "Slay a total of 15 Gowngoats or Boggi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Soyeux ou tachet\u00E9 ?",
        "Client": "Demoiselle en d\u00E9tresse",
        "Description": "J\u0027essaie de confectionner une\r\nnouvelle robe ressemblant \u00E0\r\nun monstre ! Que devrais-je\r\nchoisir, le Ch\u00E8vrecape soyeux\r\nou le joli Boggi tachet\u00E9 ?\r\nVa les voir, s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt !",
        "Target": "Tuer un total de 15 Ch\u00E8vrecape\r\nou Boggi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Morbido o pezzato?",
        "Client": "Lady in pericolo",
        "Description": "Sto cercando di ideare un\r\nnuovo vestito, e voglio basarlo\r\nsu di una creatura! Sar\u00E0 una\r\nTunicapra o forse un Boggi?\r\nCosa posso scegliere?\r\nVai ad aiutarmi, ti prego!",
        "Target": "Uccidi 15 Tunicapre o Boggi in totale",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Weich oder gefleckt?",
        "Client": "Dame in Not",
        "Description": "Ich \u00FCberlege mir gerade ein\r\nDesign f\u00FCr ein neues Kleid. Es\r\nsoll auf einem Monster basieren!\r\nDer flauschigen Gewandziege\r\noder dem niedlich gefleckten\r\nBoggi? Welchen soll ich w\u00E4hlen?!\r\nGeh und sie sieh dir an!",
        "Target": "Erlege insgesamt 15 Gewandziegen\r\noder Boggi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00BFBlandito o circulitos?",
        "Client": "Damisela en apuros",
        "Description": "Estoy dise\u00F1ando un vestido,\r\n\u00A1y quiero tomar a una criatura\r\ncomo inspiraci\u00F3n! A cu\u00E1l deber\u00EDa\r\nelegir, \u00A1\u00BFa la esponjosa Capabra,\r\no al Boggi y sus topitos?!\r\n\u00A1No me decido! \u00A1Ve a echarles\r\nun vistazo, por favor!",
        "Target": "Abate un total de\r\n15 Capabra o Boggi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0443\u0448\u0438\u0441\u0442\u044B\u0439 \u0438\u043B\u0438 \u043F\u044F\u0442\u043D\u0438\u0441\u0442\u044B\u0439?",
